tive program sep he currently serves on the board of directors of cavium inc mr mehrotra holds more than  patents and has published articles in the areas of nonvolatile memory design and flash memory systems micron technology inc  sanjay mehrotra media kit global china italy japan malaysia singapore taiwan uk usa global all micron product information and support are provided on the micron global website micronmicron tutte le informazioni sui prodotti micron e il loro supporto sono disponibili sul sito globale di micron investor relations micron blogs jobs contact sales network sign up login recommended results see all search results for  search enter your fbga code to search for your part please enter a fbga code fbga code to find a model for a specific part enter the part number or choose a technology no part found or family technology add email google linkedin twitter facebook add bookmarks to cancel email bookmarks shared successfully please provide at least one email address to email addresses comma separated note optional send me a copy cancel home about news and events media relations media kits sanjay mehrotra media kit sanjay mehrotra media kit media kits about micron media kit sanjay mehrotra media kit sumit sadana media kit jeff verheul media kit micron solidscale platform architecture media kit  sata ssd media kit d xpoint technology media kit d nand client ssds media kit d nand media kit mobile d nand media kit micron and semi partner to host high tech u media kit hybrid memory cube samples available media kit altera fpga board showcases hmc media kit elpida is now micron media kit micron welcomes new president and ceo sanjay mehrotra mark durcan welcomes new president and ceo sanjay mehrotra to micron in this video introduction moving forward with new leadership view larger image    micron’s board of directors has appointed sanjay mehrotra as micron president and ceo and as a member of the board sanjay brings an outstanding track record of business success and exceptional knowledge of the memory and storage industry most recently he served as president and ceo of sandisk where he had a long and distinguished career starting as a cofounder of the company he led sandisk from startup in  until its eventual sale to western digital in  this appointment follows mark durcan’s february announcement of his desire to retire as micron’s ceo mark has stepped down but will serve as an advisor to the company until early august  micron is pleased to welcome sanjay to our team and excited to have his leadership and vision as we continue to accelerate micron’s technology position and the delivery of new and innovative products to our customers sanjay mehrotra’s background cofounder of sandisk corporation leading the company from startup in  until its eventual sale to western digital in  served as president and ceo of sandisk from  to  led sandisk team that pioneered a diversified and comprehensive portfolio of flash storage solutions that included removable products embedded mobile solutions client and enterprise solid state drives and innovative enterprise system solutions  initiated and guided a highly successful year joint venture partnership with toshiba in nand flash memory technology development and manufacturing     held design engineering positions at integrated device technology inc seeq technology and intel corporation    earned bachelors and masters degrees in electrical engineering and computer sciences from the university of california berkeley and graduated from the stanford graduate school of business executive program sep  holds more than  patents and has published articles in the area of nonvolatile memory design and flash memory systems read the press release micron leadership image gallery faqs q why was the search for a new ceo initiated  a  mark durcan had discussed with the board of directors his desire to retire from micron when the time and conditions were right for the company as a result the board formed a special committee to oversee the selection process for the position of ceo and with the assistance of a leading global executive search firm initiated a search to identify and vet candidates  q  why was sanjay mehrotra chosen what strengths does he bring to micron a  sanjay mehrotra was selected because his track record of business success exceptional knowledge of the memory and storage industry and experience in markets ranging from consumer to enterprise make him uniquely qualified to lead micron into the future as a cofounder of sandisk mehrotra led the company from startup in  until its eventual sale in  additionally he served as sandisk’s president and ceo from  to     q  what is the timing of the transition will there be overlap between durcan and mehrotra a  the board of directors has announced that mehrotra will join micron effective may  as the new president and ceo durcan will step down as ceo and from the micron board of directors on may  but he will continue in an advisory role until early august to ensure a seamless and effective transition  q  will mehrotra be on micron’s board of directors  a  yes mehrotra will join the micron board of directors effective may    q   do you anticipate major changes in direction for micron with the new leader a   the board is not looking to revise micron’s direction but rather to ensure we continue to invest in areas of the business that will accelerate micron’s market and technology position and enable timely delivery of new and innovative products  the board continually evaluates the company’s strategy in light of the competitive landscape by implementing a longterm succession plan the board aims to ensure a smooth transition and position micron for continued success in the future  q   where will mehrotra be located will micron’s headquarters remain in boise a   mehrotra will work out of both the milpitas and boise offices micron has no plans to move its headquarters from boise contacts corporate media inquiries marc musgrove tel   media relations email media relations micron technology inc mail stop   south federal way po box  boise id  sanjay mehrotra  wikipedia sanjay mehrotra from wikipedia the free encyclopedia jump to navigation search this biography of a living person needs additional citations for verification please help by adding reliable sources contentious material about living persons that is unsourced or poorly sourced must be removed immediately especially if potentially libelous or harmful june  learn how and when to remove this template message sanjay mehrotra is cofounder of sandisk and served as the companys president and chief executive officer until it was purchased by western digital in  in april  it was announced mehrotra would be the next ceo of micron technology taking over from mark durcan contents  founding  education  awards  activities  references foundingedit mehrotra cofounded sandisk in  and served as president and ceo from  until  he previously served as executive vice president and chief operating officer senior vice president of engineering vice president of product development and director of memory design and product engineering he has more than  years of experience in the nonvolatile semiconductor memory industry including engineering and management positions at sandisk micron integrated device technology seeq technology intel corporation and atmel corporationcitation needed educationedit mehrotra spent a few years of his early education in a delhi school sardar patel vidyalaya lodhi road he started college at bits pilani and then transferred to university of california berkeley mehrotra was awarded his bachelors and masters degrees in electrical engineering and computer sciences by berkeley he is a  graduate of the stanford university graduate school of businesses executive education programcitation needed mehrotra holds more than  patents he has published articles in the area of nonvolatile memory design and flash memory systemscitation needed awardsedit mehrotra has received the following awards and honors mehrotra was honored by the american india foundation for “personal philanthropic efforts and for leading sandisk’s programs to advance educational opportunities for young people from disadvantaged backgrounds march   “distinguished lifetime achievement award” from the chinese institute of engineers usa at the th annual asian american engineer of the year award ceremony march   ceo of the year” from the entrepreneur’s foundation of silicon valley in recognition of his leadership in advancing sandisk’s community service activities december   distinguished alumni award in electrical engineering” from the university of california berkeley  “ieee reynold b johnson data storage device technology award” with sandisk cofounders ei harari and jack yuan for “leadership in the development and commercialization of flash electrically erasable programmable readonly memorybased data storage products”  activitiesedit mehrotra delivered a commencement address to graduates of the university of california berkeley college of engineering on may   his speech detailed his own journey and related the lessons he has learned along the way from being an international student to the head of a fortune  companycitation needed on april   mehrotra along with s shankar sastry dean and carlson professor of engineering at uc berkeley opened the sandisk computing lab college of engineering at the university of california berkeley the lab was funded by a  million donation by sandisk to the college of engineering the donation also funded recently completed renovations to cory hall home of the college’s department of electrical engineering and computer sciencescitation needed referencesedit  sandisk announces planned retirement of chairman and ceo eli harari sandisk  retrieved    a b tallis billy  april  micron hires new ceo sanjay mehrotra sandisk cofounder and former ceo anandtech retrieved  april    qa sandisk ceo sanjay mehrotr