of semiconductorbased data storage acquisitionsedit in october  sandisk acquired matrix semiconductor in july  sandisk acquired msystems in may  sandisk acquired pilant technology a manufacturer of solid state drives for us million in february  sandisk acquired flashsoft in june  sandisk acquired schooner information technology developer of the flashoptimized database software schoonersql and caching software membrain in july  sandisk acquired smart storage systems a producer of ssds for the enterprise market for us million in june  sandisk acquired fusionio a producer of flash memory for enterprise datacenters for  billion awards and recognitionedit in  sandisk cofounder dr eli harari won the national medal of technology and innovation from president barack obama for his innovations and contributions to flash memory storage solutions in  the enough project ranked sandisk the third highest of  consumer electronics companies on progress on conflict minerals other products and technologiesedit sandisk extreme  portable ssd gb front and back sandisk extreme pro sd uhsii usbc reader companies portal san francisco bay area portal flashcp secure usb drive startkey u sandisk sansa eyefi ulltradimm referencesedit  market view nand flash brand supplier revenue falls  in first quarter dramexchange  retrieved    western digital to acquire sandisk for b usa today gannett company october   retrieved october     western digital officially closes sandisk acquisition the verge vox media may   retrieved august     harris scott duke  mercury news interview sandisk ceo helped launch digital revolution the san jose mercury news retrieved    santa clara valley chapter meeting future directions for semiconductor nonvolatile memory santa clara university ieee electron devices society january     sandisk to acquire matrix semiconductor cnet retrieved  august    sandisk to buy msystems the street  archived from the original on  retrieved    sandisk plans to buy ssd maker pliant technology c